(9, 'Home', '&lt;p style="margin-left: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; font-family: Georgia;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;The BCC was constructed on the bottom of the ridge leading to the small fishing &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;village&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt; of &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Kaole&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;, home of the famous Ruins. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-left: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; font-family: Georgia;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;The hotel cascades down a slope with the 10 comfortable rooms on the highest level to the swimming p&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;ool and restaurant area on the beach front.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; There is a unique view of the Z&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;anzibar Channel all the way to&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Lazy Lagoon Peninsular&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt; and&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt; across the bay to the mangrove forests at &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Livingstone&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;Village&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-left: 0pt; margin-right: 0pt; font-family: Georgia;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;This\r\nfamily run business was built up with a love of the never ending\r\nviews,&amp;nbsp; nature in its entirety, peace and quiet, a respect for the\r\nlocal culture and a desire to be different.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; If you are looking for\r\nshops, discos and nightlife&amp;nbsp; â€“ then this is not for you.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&am